Simple Dockerfile for Evan Keane's DESTROY single-pulse search software.

Original Software: https://github.com/evanocathain/destroy_gutted

Dockerfile built based on AMBER AA-ALERT Dockerfile:

https://github.com/AA-ALERT/AMBER_docker

------------------

Instructions to build image:

1) Copy Dockerfile into desired directory
2) type 'docker build .' within desired directory
3) locate IMAGE ID by typing 'docker images'
4) rename the docker something meaningful with 'docker tag [IMAGE ID] [NAME]'
6) run image with 'docker run -it [NAME]'

OR

7) mount to a location within your computer using 'docker run -it -v [LOCATION]/:[LOCATION] [NAME]'
